parameters.signature:
A character string containing the bake for the signature
challenge for that baker/episode.
parameters.showstopper:
A character string containing the bake for the
showstopper challenge for that baker/episode.
parameters.episode: An integer denoting episode number within a series.
parameters.baker: A character string with a given name or nickname.
parameters.technical:
An integer denoting the rank on the technical challenge
for that baker/episode. A value of 1 means the baker was the winner of
the technical challenge. If NA, the baker did not appear in the
episode.

description:
Description
Bakes for both the signature and showstopper challenges for each baker
across all 10 GBBO series.
title: Bakes (raw)
format:
A data frame with 548 rows representing individual signatures and
